
- Make a run/ directory
- Take BART.cfg files from the examples/ directory
- Edit the configuration file and put it in run/ directory
- cd to run/ directory
- Run BART with: ../BART.py

- To execute just the Atmospheric file section (TEA), run:
  ../BART.py --justTEA

- To execute just up to the Opacity calculation section, run:
  ../BART.py --justOpacity
